---
title: Easy Hawaiian Bacon & Pineapple Tortilla Pizza with Smoked Cheddar Cheese & Deluxe Salad
description: A regular debate we have at HelloFresh is whether or not pineapple should go on a pizza. This recipe is obviously for anyone
who's on Team Pineapple. The fruit's sweetness and tanginess is a lovely contrast to the salty, umami-rich bacon.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6479b1d5566de4b9070ed35e-c60681d6.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/6479b1d5566de4b9070ed35e.pdf
